158
00:10:15.260 --> 00:10:18.920
If I could just provide some feedback that setting up a

159
00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:20.100
new offense

160
00:10:21.540 --> 00:10:24.360
that health practitioners may be subject to-

161
00:10:24.840 --> 00:10:25.020
Yeah

162
00:10:25.030 --> 00:10:25.030
...

163
00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:29.200
supporters of this bill will need to have a, including myself-

164
00:10:29.340 --> 00:10:29.660
Yes

165
00:10:29.670 --> 00:10:31.180
